see what's inside.

01:24.475 --> 01:26.434
I don't give a fuck
how they dig it out.

01:26.564 --> 01:30.090
- You don't wanna see
what's inside, I promise you.

01:30.220 --> 01:31.874
- Mike, you know about this?

01:32.004 --> 01:33.745
- I don't even know
what the fuck this is.

01:33.876 --> 01:35.878
- Did Mitch?
- No.

01:36.008 --> 01:39.142
- Is that a you're sure no
or you hope no?

01:39.273 --> 01:41.101
- I hope no.

01:41.231 --> 01:42.798
- Well, that's fucking great.

01:42.928 --> 01:45.322
- Yeah.
- Yeah, real fucking great.

01:45.453 --> 01:47.585
- Explain to me
how you found this.

01:47.716 --> 01:50.066
- It's, uh, Milo
said metal case.

01:50.197 --> 01:52.677
So I got a metal detector.
That's what I found.

01:52.808 --> 01:54.418
- Pretty big case,
wouldn't you say?

01:54.549 --> 01:58.596
- Yeah. I don't think this is
what he wanted me to find.

01:58.727 --> 02:00.381
- [bird squawking]

02:00.511 --> 02:03.340
- Homicide, you're up.

02:03.471 --> 02:05.255
- Here we go,
gentlemen, let's do it.

02:05.386 --> 02:10.739
