Fuck this.

02:22.620 --> 02:24.883
- [bird squawking]

02:28.539 --> 02:32.152
- [glass shattering]

02:34.676 --> 02:36.068
- Fucking Jesus Christ!

02:36.199 --> 02:37.983
- [coughing]

02:38.114 --> 02:39.289
- Shit! Mike?
- Yeah?

02:39.420 --> 02:41.204
- You got any smokes?
- Shit.

02:41.335 --> 02:44.164
- [coughing]

02:46.427 --> 02:48.298
- This fucking job...

02:54.174 --> 02:56.219
[grunts]

02:58.526 --> 03:00.876
- [glass crunching]

03:06.795 --> 03:09.058
- [coughs]

