- [rats squeaking]

03:36.781 --> 03:38.696
- Aw, fuck me!

03:42.787 --> 03:46.313
- [coughing]

03:48.619 --> 03:52.362
- [retches, coughs]

04:02.372 --> 04:05.767
[pants]

04:05.897 --> 04:07.421
- Hey.

04:08.813 --> 04:10.598
You all right?

04:10.728 --> 04:15.646
- No, Mike.
I'm not all right.

04:15.777 --> 04:18.170
[coughs]

