- I count 26.

04:22.871 --> 04:25.526
- You count 26 what?

04:25.656 --> 04:27.441
- STEVIE: Twenty-six bodies.

04:31.706 --> 04:34.752
- I'd put the crime
photographer in a Hazmat suit,

04:34.883 --> 04:36.319
get him to just
video this scene.

04:36.450 --> 04:39.627
Then we get the coroner's
office, move the bodies.

04:39.757 --> 04:42.282
We do our initial finds
at the fucking morgue.

04:45.241 --> 04:46.895
- We should do it here.

04:47.025 --> 04:51.726
- I'm not going in that
fucking thing again, all right?

04:51.856 --> 04:54.468
You want it done
here, you do it.

04:56.948 --> 04:59.516
That's what I thought.
Stevie? Let's go.

