the leaders of the blacks,

17:01.585 --> 17:05.372
the whites, and the Mafia
have a 30-minute pow-wow.

17:05.502 --> 17:08.636
No soldiers with them.
No posturing.

17:08.766 --> 17:10.507
You know what it means when
rival gangs group together

17:10.638 --> 17:14.250
with no soldiers watching, Mike?
You know what it means.

17:14.381 --> 17:19.168
