talking about us.

17:19.299 --> 17:20.996
- Think they're
planning a takeover?

17:21.127 --> 17:22.911
- That's exactly what I think.

17:23.042 --> 17:24.826
- Okay, well, lock it down.

17:24.956 --> 17:27.437
- I can't lock them down.

17:27.568 --> 17:29.961
Fucking warden's on a feel good.

17:30.092 --> 17:33.269
- Well, then you know
what to do, Ed, right?

17:33.400 --> 17:35.445
Press record,
film it, show it to him.

17:35.576 --> 17:36.838
Done.

17:36.968 --> 17:39.188
- He thinks he made peace.

17:39.319 --> 17:41.234
- What do you want me to do?

17:41.364 --> 17:42.670
- [prison yard chatter]

17:42.800 --> 17:45.847
- Check their temperature
and get back to me.

17:52.593 --> 17:55.030
- [text whoosh, chime]
- Sorry, Mike.

17:55.161 --> 17:56.640
I hope you didn't miss too much.

17:56.771 --> 17:58.729
- That's the thing
about bad news, right?

17:58.860 --> 18:00.383
No matter how long you wait,
it's gonna be right there

18:00.514 --> 18:02.951
waiting for you.
- [text chime]

18:03.082 --> 18:05.301
- Look--oh, wait,
here, take this.

18:05.432 --> 18:06.781
- Ugh, thank god.

18:06.911 --> 18:08.870
- The feeling's
mutual, by the way.

